channel.description: When I click on my CFG files and the files pop-up and I open it takes me to this website. http://noeld.com/download.htm#DynSite. I dont know how to download it can anyone help me out. Or has something that wouuld work for the server.

item.description:
@pizza_pie wrote:

alright, just go right click > properties, look at where it says “Opens with:” it should say some kind of program, there should be a button next to it that says change, press it, and chose notepad or wordpad or textpad, whichever one you have… its not that difficult!
